          Não deixe <span style="font-weight: 700;">seu dinheiro</span><br />
          falando sozinho
        </h1>

        <div class="mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-[35.372px] text-white leading-[1.1]" style="font-family: 'SF Pro', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;">Captura de economias</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-white text-lg lg:text-[24.488px] mb-8 max-w-xl leading-[1.1]" style="font-family: 'SF Pro', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 200;">
          Identificamos automaticamente onde você pode economizar
        </p>

        <a href="#" class="bg-white text-[#1b329a] px-10 py-4 rounded-full text-[24.891px] hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1" style="font-family: 'SF Pro', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">
          Começar agora →
        </a>

        <!-- Dots indicator -->
        <div class="flex gap-2 mt-8">
          <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-white/40 rounded-full"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-white/40 rounded-full"></span>
        </div>

